request command

    (A) FUNCTION
        Request command shows a list of facilities being under the
        request functionality, enables or disables the request
        functionality.
        
    (B) SYNOPSIS

         request  [ "on" | "off" ]

    (C) PARAMETERS
        on
         enables whole of the requests.

        off
         disables whole of the requests.

        (without any parameters)
         The list of facilities subject to the requesting is put out
         to speaking-stream.

    (D) NOTES
        The requesting is disabled on SECONDS' startup.

    (E) SEE ALSO
        req_add command
        req_rmv command
